== Introduction ==

This is a command-line interface for oVirt Virtualization.

== Installation ==

NOTE: ovirt-shell depends on ovirt-engine-sdk, 

Installation from the source directory:

 $ python setup.py build
 # python setup.py install

== Usage ==

ovirt-shell comes with an extensive only help system. To start out, use:

 $ ovirt-shell --help
 $ ovirt-shell
